    <div class="main review-item" id="6339353">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6339353/" class="title-link">《乱时候，穷时候》：主宰时光</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6339353"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/mysteryland/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2696818-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mysteryland/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">暗蓝色的海</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-20"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-20 17:26:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6339353_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  秋意渐浓，似乎又要到围炉读书的冬夜时光了。 古人似乎很喜欢在冬天时“围炉夜话”，究其原因，大概是冬日里农事基本已毕，而物质条件又不允许有其他娱乐活动，无论在室外还是室内。 想象一下，这样的时光未免太惬意，你不必为了上网是网速不给力而揪心，不必为8点档电视剧的坑...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6339353/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6339353_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6339353_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





